programs.name: Yaws - Current status questionnaire
programs.description: The purpose of this questionnaire is to gather baseline information from Member states to help WHO plan the implementation of the resolutions of the WHA66.12 and the Regional Committee for Africa (AFR/RC63/R6) to eradicate yaws by 2020.
